Title: Nonparametric Local Linear Smoothing
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Nicholas Hartman
Maintainer: Nicholas Hartman <nhar@umich.edu>
Description: Fits two of the most popular local linear smoothers using nonparametric estimation: LOESS (Cleveland, 1979) and Friedman's super smoother (Friedman, 1984).
